"'''Nerf Herder'''" is a comic that was published in ''[[Star Wars Tales 7]]''.

==Plot summary==
The main character, [[Domo Jones]], a young [[Nerf herder/Legends|nerf herder]] from [[Tatooine/Legends|Tatooine]], decides to help the [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Alliance to Restore the Republic]] by sabotaging an [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] purchase of [[Proton torpedo/Legends|proton torpedoes]]. He enlists the help of the [[Twi'lek/Legends|Twi'lek]] waitress [[JillJoo Jab]], the [[Protocol droid/Legends|protocol droid]] [[UR-1]], and the [[Bith/Legends|Bith]] musician [[Blerx Tango|Blerx]]. Successful in foiling the Imperial plot, Jiljoo and Domo share a kiss at the end of the story.

